    <div class="title">The relationship between the proportion of frugivorous bird species and altitude.</div>
   </div>
   <div xlink:href="pone.0150498.g005" class="graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
  </div>
  <div id="pone.0150498.g006" orientation="portrait" position="float" class="fig" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
